<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes. At least where I live. I get all books from the library because I live in 236 sq ft and there is ZERO room for a toothpick. You can even get the <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes. At least where I live. I get all books from the library because I live in 236 sq ft and there is ZERO room for a toothpick. You can even get the e version for Kindle or any other ebook software. Libraries have their own now (called Libby where I live). You can download it from library websites.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
