<span id="freeTextContainer15611058520428204119">4.5<br/>You know how some books just fill an emotional need that you are having at the time?<br/>Well, this book did just that for me.<br/>It had a real wholesomeness and utter goodness that I so needed at the time. It is not perfect but it has some good, caring people and I enjoyed this book so much. I think you will enjoy it too.</span>

